ad hoc

Reboot = absible myServer -a "/sbin/reboot"

Transfer a File = ansible atlanta -m ansible.builtin.copy -a "src=/etc/hosts dest=/tmp/hosts"

Check if a Package is Installed = ansible webservers -m ansible.builtin.yum -a "name=acme state=present"

Pass sudo password in order to run updates = ansible-playbook server_updates.yaml -i inventory.ini --ask-become-passThen run this 3 times and provide password of all 3 nodes one at a time.


